# event-guide
Event Guide manages the data for conference mobile apps to give information to guests.

# Group Events
Events related resources of the **Event Guide API**

## Events Collection [/events.json]
### List all Events [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [{
          "id": 1,
          "name": "IHG Conference",
          "pages": { }
        }]

### Show an Event [GET]

+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) Numeric `id` of the event.

